Megatron notted Blindchaos' lack of vigor for a fight, as he viewed the
computer screen. Autofire was doing an admirable job, and Megatron was
feeling confident now. Megatron turned towards them. "Dominjoe, your
mission is to get out there, and simply stall any Decepticons not
belonging to me. Do not put yourself at risk, just buy me time. When I
am ready, i will give you a message." he then turned to Blindchaos.
"Blindchaos, you will watch my back." Megatron said with a smile.
